The paper deals with communication over a fading channel powered by an energy harvesting transmitter, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also considers optimization problems and algorithms for maximizing throughput, energy, and minimizing completion time, which are topics related to control systems (cs.SY) and multimedia (cs.MM).
